items.description: A lightweight Python bot that relays messages between a Discord server and a Meshtastic LoRa network. Use commands like !send, !broadcast, and !nodes to send/receive messages to/from specific nodes or all nodes in the mesh. Runs in a single script with direct serial connection to a Meshtastic device for seamless two-way communication.
